member.name: F:CloudinaryDotNet.Actions.Role.Admin
member.summary: Same as a master admin, except that they do not have access to account management, billing details and purchase/upgrade options.

member.name: F:CloudinaryDotNet.Actions.Role.Billing
member.summary: Can access only billing-related areas of the Cloudinary management console, including the Billing tab (for paid accounts), usage reports, and purchase/upgrade options.

member.name: F:CloudinaryDotNet.Actions.Role.TechnicalAdmin
member.summary: Same as an Admin, except they do not have access to the List of users area of the User Settings.

member.name: F:CloudinaryDotNet.Actions.Role.Reports
member.summary: Can access only reporting details in the Cloudinary console, including those in the Dashboard and in the Reports tabs.

member.name: F:CloudinaryDotNet.Actions.Role.MediaLibraryAdmin
member.summary: Full read-write access to all areas of the Cloudinary console that are related to asset management.

member.name: F:CloudinaryDotNet.Actions.Role.MediaLibraryUser
member.summary: Can access only the Media Library area of the console. The specific read, write, and other access permissions that a user has within the Media Library are controlled by the user groups that the user belongs to and the folders that are shared with those user groups.
